node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jason Oppenheim on September 02, 2021. May be an image of furniture, sky and text that says 'THE OPPENHEIM GROUP REAL ESTATE 8700 FRANKLIN AVE. SUNSET ÛSRP STRIP OFFERED AT $4,695,000 JUTD JUST LISTED'.

node.text:
Just Listed - 8700 Franklin Ave. - $4,695,000

3 Beds / 3 Baths / 2,766 Sq. Ft. / 16,384 Lot Size

Situated on its own promontory just above the Sunset Strip, this serene and private home features unrivaled jetliner panoramic views of the entire city and Hollywood Hills. The pool and outdoor patio evoke feelings of a five-star resort, with an additional waterfall, spa, and fire pit providing seamless indoor/outdoor flow. Enter through the unique front door to the open floor plan with a gorgeous living room, vaulted wood-beamed ceilings, see-through fireplace, and a dining area with incredible views from every room. The sleek kitchen is complete with modern, stainless steel appliances. An additional bedroom, bathroom, and laundry room complete the main floor.  A custom steel wall and floating staircase lead below to a large seating area and owner’s suite overlooking the entire city, replete with a luxurious spa-like bathroom including a walk-in shower with benches for sitting, all opening to a massive deck. The third bedroom with an ensuite bath has floor-to-ceiling sliding doors perfect for an office or extra guest room. Detached 2-car garage and 2 uncovered parking spaces.

node.text:
Just Listed in Corona Del Mar - 215 Milford Dr.
Offered at: $5,299,000

Beds: 4
Baths: 6
Square Footage: 6,500
Lot Size: 15,084 sq. ft.

A unique development opportunity in Cameo Shores with ocean and canyon views. The project has been beautifully designed by renowned @tagfront and boasts a contemporary open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 6 bathrooms, a gym with a sauna, a movie theatre, and a large private yard/deck with pool and sunken fire pit. 3-car garage. The square footage is an estimation; the final square footage will be based upon city approval.
